    <div align="center"> Dictionary.
    <div align="left"> [1] <a href="https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/dogma"> Dogma </a>: A set of beliefs that is believed without doubt or question.
    <div align="left"> [2] <a href="https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/ethic"> Ethic </a>: Relating to beliefs about what is wrong and right. 
